# This placeholder makes internal/web/dist/ exist in dev so the
# //go:embed all:dist directive compiles. The real React build is
# written here at image-build time (see the frontend-build stage in
# Dockerfile). In dev dist/ contains only this file, so web.Handler()
# returns a 404 handler and the master serves no frontend — devs hit
# the Vite dev server on :5173 instead.
